WEBVTT

00:03.093 --> 00:03.748
<i>A few years back</i>

00:03.786 --> 00:04.888
<i>a reporter figured out</i>

00:04.926 --> 00:06.644
<i>what I do at the DA's office.</i>

00:06.728 --> 00:08.729
<i>There was a big scandal.</i>

00:11.116 --> 00:14.068
<i>I lost my job for a while.</i>

00:14.136 --> 00:17.405
<i>My boss lost his job</i>
<i>for a while.</i>

00:17.456 --> 00:21.242
<i>Finally, I got my job back,</i>

00:21.310 --> 00:23.844
<i>but now my name was out there,</i>

00:23.912 --> 00:27.315
<i>and that's when I started</i>
<i>to get letters.</i>

00:27.382 --> 00:30.084
<i>Letters</i>
<i>from all over the country,</i>

00:30.152 --> 00:32.953
<i>all over the world,</i>

00:33.005 --> 00:35.789
<i>from people who wanted my help.</i>

00:35.841 --> 00:39.093
<i>More letters</i>
<i>than I could possibly read.</i>

00:39.144 --> 00:41.896
<i>More letters</i>
<i>than I could possibly answer.</i>

00:41.963 --> 00:43.964
Hey.

00:44.032 --> 00:47.068
I'm only one person.

00:47.135 --> 00:50.905
Hey. I can't breathe!

00:53.041 --> 00:55.009
Oh. Hey, you okay?

00:55.043 --> 00:56.944
Need some water
or something?

00:57.012 --> 00:59.880
I don't know.
No, I'm okay.

00:59.948 --> 01:02.649
I just had a dream.
I just had a ridiculous dream.

01:02.701 --> 01:04.001
It was about the mail.

01:04.086 --> 01:06.987
Any particular male?

01:07.055 --> 01:09.156
No, dear.

01:09.224 --> 01:12.960
You're the only male
I ever dream about.

01:13.028 --> 01:15.963
Good answer. Feel free
to keep dreaming.

